setStreetViewEnabled

public final void setStreetViewEnabled(boolean streetViewEnabled)
Enables or disables user-initiated entry to Street View imagery. When true, the Pegman icon is present in the navigation controls, allowing a user to drag the Pegman onto a street to initiate Street View. Users can also zoom down to ground level to enter Street View when this is set to true.

Parameters:
streetViewEnabled -

public final boolean getStreetViewEnabled()
Returns:
Whether Street View is enabled in the navigation controls.
